docs.text: HOLA ¶ I am José Hirmas Stark. Chilean. Social entrepreneur. Business designer. Educator. Grandson of immigrants: Palestinian descent from my father, Hungarian from my mother. Interested in: - the power of human relationships for educational development and justice - designing business projects that generate positive social outcomes - theater and acting as a communicational tool for developing your attitude - good food and craft beer taster
